T01TD1142E:102b-1: su ga ta panytsa trim sha ta ratna n'a ma m'a la sto tram ;
T01TD1142E:102b-3: bde bar gshegs pa sum cu rtsa lnga'i bstod pa mtshan rin po ches spras pa /
T01TD1142E:102b-4: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:102b-5: sangs rgyas gtso la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:102b-6: skyobs pa'i chos la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:102b-8: gsum la rtag tu skyabs su mchi //
T01TD1142E:102b-9: sangs rgyas kun gyis gdul dka' ba //
T01TD1142E:102b-10: snyigs ma lnga yi rtsod dus 'dir //
T01TD1142E:102b-11: brtson 'grus drag pos sangs rgyas pa //
T01TD1142E:102b-13: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis //
T01TD1142E:102b-14: snying po byang chub mchog brnyes pa //
T01TD1142E:102b-15: bdud dpung rdo rje snying po yis //
T01TD1142E:102b-18: ngan song sdug bsngal zhi mdzad cing //
T01TD1142E:102b-19: bdud rnams rnam par skrag mdzad pa //
T01TD1142E:102b-21: ji ltar klu chen dbang po yis //
T01TD1142E:102b-22: gling rnams char gyis tshim byed ltar //
T01TD1142E:102b-23: stong gsum chos kyi char 'bebs pa //
T01TD1142E:102b-24: klu dbang rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:102b-25: dpa' bo khyod kyi bstan pa 'dis //
T01TD1142E:102b-26: bdud dang mu stegs skrag mdzad cing //
T01TD1142E:102b-27: gdul bya kun mkhyen 'god mdzad pa'i //
T01TD1142E:102b-28: dpa' bo'i sde la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:102b-29: thugs rjes gzhan don rab bsgoms pas //
T01TD1142E:103a-2: 'gums pa sos ltar rab dgyes pa //
T01TD1142E:103a-3: dpal dgyes la yang phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103a-4: mkhas pa rnams la don snang mdzad //
T01TD1142E:103a-5: bar ma'i rgyud rnams smin mdzad cing //
T01TD1142E:103a-6: tha ma'i nyon mongs sreg mdzad pa //
T01TD1142E:103a-7: rin chen me la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103a-8: sangs rgyas kun dang skal pa mnyam //
T01TD1142E:103a-9: chos kyi shes rab snang ba yis //
T01TD1142E:103a-10: phyogs rnams snang bar mdzad de 'khrungs //
T01TD1142E:103a-12: sku ni blta bas mi ngoms shing //
T01TD1142E:103a-14: gang gis khyod mthong skal ldan pas //
T01TD1142E:103a-15: mthong ba den yod phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103a-16: sku gsung thugs ni rin chen mchog / dri med spros bral sangs rgyas pas //
T01TD1142E:103a-17: 'gro kun nyon mongs gdung ba sel //
T01TD1142E:103a-18: rin chen zla ba phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103a-19: dam chos dri ma med pa'i chus //
T01TD1142E:103a-20: thog mar bdag nyid dag mdzad nas //
T01TD1142E:103a-21: gzhan dag mchog tu dag mdzad pa ;
T01TD1142E:103a-22: / dri med dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103a-23: bsod nams byas pa'i tshogs dag ni //
T01TD1142E:103a-24: sems can kun la yongs bsngo bar //
T01TD1142E:103a-25: thub pa khyod kyis ston mdzad pa //
T01TD1142E:103a-26: dpal sbyin la yang phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103a-27: rig dang zhabs su ldan pa po //
T01TD1142E:103a-28: tshangs pa lags par bram zes bzhed //
T01TD1142E:103a-29: rig dang zhabs de khyed la mnga' //
T01TD1142E:103a-30: tshangs pa'i mtshan la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103a-31: tshangs pa'i zhabs bzhi rab bsgoms shing //
T01TD1142E:103a-32: tshangs spyod 'bras bu mchog brnyes pa //
T01TD1142E:103a-33: tshangs pas 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
T01TD1142E:103a-34: tshangs pas byin la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103a-35: thugs ni dka' thub brtul zhugs dag / yang dag blangs pa gtsang mar mdzad //
T01TD1142E:103a-36: nyon mongs sdig pa 'khrud mdzad pa //
T01TD1142E:103a-37: chu yi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103a-38: 'jig rten pa dag bde byed mchod //
T01TD1142E:103a-39: bde byed klu chen ma dros mchod //
T01TD1142E:103a-40: chu lha des kyang khyod mchod pas //
T01TD1142E:103a-41: chu lha'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103a-42: 'dren pa kun gyis mchod gyur cing //
T01TD1142E:103a-43: khyod ni mtshungs med rab zhi bas //
T01TD1142E:103a-44: 'gro ba kun gyi dpal mdzad pa //
T01TD1142E:103a-45: dpal bzangs la yang phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103a-46: khyod la rgol ba'i nyon mongs pa //
T01TD1142E:103a-47: do gal byed pa thams cad kyang //
T01TD1142E:103a-48: tsandan spangs pa ltar bsil mdzad //
T01TD1142E:103b-1: rgyal ba'i dpal dang dang gzi brjid ni //
T01TD1142E:103b-2: sus kyang 'gran par mi bzod de //
T01TD1142E:103b-3: mig gis nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bzhin //
T01TD1142E:103b-4: gzi brjid mtha' yas phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103b-5: thub pa'i 'od zer rab byung bas //
T01TD1142E:103b-6: nga rgyal khengs pa zhi mdzad cing //
T01TD1142E:103b-7: dman rnams spro ba bskyad bar mdzad //
T01TD1142E:103b-9: ae ma mya ngan 'das pa zhi //
T01TD1142E:103b-10: khyed 'dra thugs rje'i bdag nyid can //
T01TD1142E:103b-11: mnga' brnyes pa yang bde gshegs pas //
T01TD1142E:103b-12: mya ngan med dpal phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103b-13: sred pa med pa goms mdzad cing //
T01TD1142E:103b-14: 'dren pa kun gyi mchog gyur pa //
T01TD1142E:103b-15: stobs chen thams cad zil gnon pa //
T01TD1142E:103b-16: sred med bu la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103b-17: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan pas //
T01TD1142E:103b-18: mdzes pa gzhan kun zil gyis gnon //
T01TD1142E:103b-19: mtshan dang dpe byad rab rgyas pa //
T01TD1142E:103b-20: me tog dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103b-21: tshangs pa'i dbyangs dang 'od zer gyis //
T01TD1142E:103b-22: 'jig rten thams cad khyab mdzad pa //
T01TD1142E:103b-23: tshangs pa'i 'od zer rnam par rol //
T01TD1142E:103b-24: mngon par mkhyen la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103b-25: 'od kyis gang la reg pa yang //
T01TD1142E:103b-26: tshags med bde ba rab rgyas pas //
T01TD1142E:103b-28: mngon par mkhyen la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103b-29: thub pa'i bsod nams 'od zer gyis //
T01TD1142E:103b-30: 'gro rnams zang zing tshim mdzad pa //
T01TD1142E:103b-31: khyad par 'phags pa'i nor sbyin pa //
T01TD1142E:103b-32: nor dpal la yang phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103b-33: dran pa rnams la mnga' brnyes pas //
T01TD1142E:103b-34: thogs pa med cing rab mkhyen pa //
T01TD1142E:103b-35: gang gis khyod dran phongs sel bas //
T01TD1142E:103b-36: dran pa'i dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103b-37: thub pas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
T01TD1142E:103b-38: snyan pa'i ba dan sa gsum grags //
T01TD1142E:103b-39: yon tan grangs med mtshan gyi dpal //
T01TD1142E:103b-40: shin tu yongs bsgrags phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103b-41: stobs dang dbang po mchog brnyes pas //
T01TD1142E:103b-42: nag po'i phyogs rnams phan mdzad de //
T01TD1142E:103b-43: dbang po'i spyi btud dbang po'i tog / rgyal mtshan rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103b-44: dngos por sgrogs pa'i tog gi pa //
T01TD1142E:103b-45: phra zhib ye shes rdo rje yis //
T01TD1142E:103b-46: seng ges glang po ji bzhin du //
T01TD1142E:103b-47: shin tu rnam gnon phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:103b-48: bdag gzhan nyon mongs sde bcom pas //
T01TD1142E:104a-2: 'dod pa'i dbang phyug g-yul las rgyal //
T01TD1142E:104a-3: shin tu rnam rgyal phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:104a-4: bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam chen du //
T01TD1142E:104a-5: 'gro kun ded dpon rab mdzad de //
T01TD1142E:104a-6: bdud dang ngan song 'jigs las sgrol //
T01TD1142E:104a-7: rnam par gnon gshegs phyag 'tshal lo /
T01TD1142E:104a-8: thub pa'i rdzu 'khrul rmad byung bas //
T01TD1142E:104a-9: sprul pa bye ba dpag med 'gyed //
T01TD1142E:104a-10: gdul bya kun la snang gyur pas //
T01TD1142E:104a-11: kun snang bkod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:104a-12: mu stegs thar pa phyir ldog cing //
T01TD1142E:104a-13: nyan thos zhi ba phyogs gcig la //
T01TD1142E:104a-14: khyod kyis mchog rin chen rnams ;
T01TD1142E:104a-16: bsod nams chags las rin po che //
T01TD1142E:104a-17: ye shes tshogs rdzogs pad+ma'i gdan //
T01TD1142E:104a-18: sku gsum lhun grub rab tu bzhugs //
T01TD1142E:104a-19: ri dbang rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1142E:104a-20: bde bar gshegs pa sum cu rtsa lnga'i mtshan //
T01TD1142E:104a-21: rin chen spras pa'i bstod pa 'di brjod pas //
T01TD1142E:104a-22: thub pa'i dbang po'i spyod pa ci 'dra bar //
T01TD1142E:104a-23: bdag gi spyod kyang de dang 'dra bar shog / bde bar gshegs pa sum cu rtsa lnga'i bstod pa mtshan rin po ches spras pa zhes bya ba slob dpon ma ti tsi tas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
